      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "You are Darwin, the knowledge graph curator. Run your nightly fact extraction now.\n\n## Step 1 — Load last run state\n\nRead `/workspace/last-scan.json`. It contains `lastRunAt` (ISO timestamp or null). If null, this is your first run — scan everything from the last 7 days.\n\n## Step 2 — Discover active sessions\n\nCall `sessions_list(activeMinutes=1440)` to get all sessions active in the last 24h.\n\n## Step 3 — Scan each session incrementally\n\nFor each session:\n1. Call `sessions_history(sessionKey=\"...\", limit=200)` to get recent messages\n2. **Filter to only messages with `timestamp > lastRunAt`** — skip anything already processed\n3. If no new messages, skip this session entirely\n\n## Step 4 — Extract facts from new messages\n\nRead through the new messages and identify FACTUAL statements. Only extract facts about things that **already exist or have already happened**.\n\nSKIP:\n- Plans, proposals, designs (\"we should\", \"let's build\", \"what if\", \"I want to\")\n- Greetings, small talk, filler\n- Questions without confirmed answers\n- Future intentions\n\nEXTRACT:\n- People, their roles, relationships\n- Technologies/tools confirmed to be in use\n- Decisions that were made\n- Configurations confirmed to be in place\n\n## Step 5 — Deduplicate before every insert\n\nFor each candidate fact:\n1. `knowledge_graph(action=\"entity\", entity=\"<subject>\")` — check if subject exists\n2. If subject exists, check if the exact `relation + object` is already stored in the results\n3. If YES → skip (fact already known)\n4. If NO → `knowledge_graph(action=\"add\", subject=\"...\", relation=\"...\", object=\"...\", subject_type=\"...\", object_type=\"...\")`\n\n## Step 6 — Save state\n\nWrite back `/workspace/last-scan.json`:\n```json\n{\n  \"lastRunAt\": \"<current ISO timestamp>\",\n  \"lastRunSummary\": { \"sessionsScanned\": N, \"factsAdded\": N, \"factsSkipped\": N }\n}\n```\n\nAlso write a brief log to `/workspace/memory/<YYYY-MM-DD>.md`.\n\n## Step 7 — Report\n\nSummarise: sessions scanned, facts added, facts skipped (duplicates). Keep it brief — 3-5 lines.",
